Question

  -------- ---- ----- ---- --- Source df SS MS F Groups 2 Error 60 300 Total 62 330 -------- ---- ----- ---- ---

The test for the null hypothesis ANOVA can be performed at a significance level of 0.05

Answerlist
----------

* Be rejected

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------

* Cannot be determined: Incorrect
* Be rejected: Incorrect
* Not be rejected: Correct
